<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok some answers for ya cause I am trying to do the quest right now.  Most ppl do the quest for the 10int bonus the staff gives.  I wouldn't recommending melee with this weapon though it's 10dmg 100dly.  But it's wizzy only and wizzies are suppose to try not to get too close to the mobs n e wayz so that doesn't really matter.  When you reach level 49 i would recommend that you turn in the items u get from the quest and get the runes for the scroll because the spell is awesome and then do the quest again to get the 10int bonus from the staff again.  There is little chance of failing in the combination but only met one person so far that failed and I don't think there is a way to lower your chances or failure.  You just have to take your chances and wish yourself luck. : ) gl all who are doing this quest.  I wouldn't recommend doing this quest til you have invis or u can wait til u have self gates to everywhere because walking is a pain.</font></td></tr></table>
